track_notes: From roadside parking on the side of the Barbondale Road. A public footpath takes you on to access land above Stone Rigg. Broken wall running over summit provides some shelter.
track_title: TRack up to Calf Top NP-022

track_notes: Park SD 6794 8616. Walk NE along road to public footpath, left through gate SD 6831 8645.  Follow to SD 6820 8694.  Bear up hill to gate SD 6817 8713. Follow vehicle tracks zig zagging steeply up grassy slopes to reach a formidable wall at SD 6743 8708. Turn Left (SW) to follow wall to corner of the field where thankfully there is a stone stile over the wall SD 6737 8690.  Now it is a simple and easy walk SW on a rough path to the summit and the Trig point.  If you cross the low fence at the summit you can use the broken wall for shelter if needed (very much so on my visit!).
